testing.system_testing.default_components

Class ParametricComponentTest

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.xqhs.util.config.Configurable

    public class ParametricComponentTest
extends net.xqhs.util.logging.Unit
    Tests the parametric component of a CompositeAgent. Creates a bare composite agent (without a platform), and adds a parametric and a test component to it. The test component intercepts agent events and prints them. The agent is asked to exit soon after creation.

    The testing component gets the name of the agent from the ParametricComponent and prints it out.

    Author:
    Andrei Olaru
